<p>
  You asked: <em>"<%= params[:question][:q]%>"</em>
</p>
<p>
  I'm going to look for things related to <%= @terms.map{|x| "<strong>#{h(x)}</strong>"}.join(' and ').html_safe %> that have <%= [@quantity].map{|x| "<strong>#{x.to_s}</strong>"}.join(' and ').html_safe %> as inputs.
</p>
<p>
  Here are a few categories that look relevant:
  <dl>
    <% @categories.each do |x| %>
      <dt><%= x[0].meta.wikiname %></dt>
      <dd>
        <%= x[1].label %><br/>
        <%= x[2].name%><br/>
        = <%= x[3].total_amount %>kg<br/>
        <%= link_to "More info", "http://discover.amee.com/categories#{x[0].path}" %>
      </dd>
    <% end %>
  </dl>
</p>